name: Ruab
content:
Ruab was a Human male smuggler who operated out of the city of Dee'ja Peak on the planet Naboo during the time of the Galactic Civil War. He was an associate of Ogden, a Human who operated out of Keren.
Ruab was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Ruab was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
